title: Uptown/Lakes, Updated, Open Kitchen, Southside Deck, Two Off Street
posting_body: ['Quality two bedroom, second floor, apartment in security fourplex.', '  Hardwood floors, modern open kitchen.', ' New range.', ' Lockable storage.', ' PLUS, two designated, off street parking spaces included -- $80 value.', '  Convenient deck right off of kitchen.', ' FREE laundry on site -- $30 value.', ' New high efficiency windows.', ' High efficiency boiler.', " Close enough to the heart of Uptown and the lakes to be near the action and half a block to 38th and Grand with Grand Cafe, Rincon38 and Victor's.", ' Total of 7 residents in the building -- mature and respectful.', ' US Internet.', ' No dogs, no smoking.', '$1,598 for two including two designated parking spaces and free laundry.', ' $1,570 for one.', ' Available October 1.', ' Open House', 'Saturday', 'August 6, 1-2:30 pm.', ' NOTICE:', 'Grand Avenue is currently under construction.', ' When coming to view, park in lot behind building.', ' Construction work will not be a problem for residents since 3721 Grand has two designated parking spaces for each apartment.', ' No fee to apply.', ' If interested and/or have questions, email reply to owner, John.']
